        <fo:inline keep-together="always"><fo:inline font-weight="bold">1.</fo:inline> Combine the shredded bread with water</fo:inline>
        <fo:inline keep-together="always"><fo:inline font-weight="bold">2.</fo:inline> In another bowl, combine the burghul with water</fo:inline>
